  "texts": [
    "Qadir (2022) examines the advantages and drawbacks of Generative AI in education.",
    "Engineering education is evolving with generative AI like ChatGPT, offering personalized learning and simulations.",
    "However, it has limitations, including biases and ethical concerns.",
    "Educators must adapt to harness AI benefits while minimizing negatives for future engineers.",
    "According to Huang et al. (2021), the increasing role of artificial intelligence (AI) in education highlights its applications in adaptive learning, teaching evaluation, and virtual classrooms."
  ]
}